@tpendragon - my colleague at Penn reached out about this issue again as the new PACSCL site will be going live soon and will likely be getting some publicity. Could I put you in touch with Penn's new IT person overseeing the site to see if this issue can be resolved? (Michael Gibney is no longer at Penn.) 

Assuming this is a related issue, but Princeton's name doesn't display on the site's list of repos: https://findingaids.library.upenn.edu/repositories.

Thanks.
